data.description:
Introducing 1257 Shady Lane, Joplin, MO - a beautiful ranch-style home that's begging for you to make it home! Situated on a peaceful .85-acre corner lot, this home offers 2,148 sq ft of living space, 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and an oversized attached 2-car garage.

Inside, you'll find a front living room with lots of natural light and a cozy fireplace. The kitchen comes equipped with all the appliances you need and plenty of cabinet space. There are 3 bedrooms and a common bathroom on the main level, along with a massive 2nd living room. The common bathroom features a jetted tub and shower, adding a touch of luxury to your daily routine.

Upstairs, you'll find a very large master bedroom suite with a custom headboard and a large walk-in closet. Convenience is key with 2 washer/dryer connections - one in the garage and another in a bedroom.

Enjoy your morning coffee in the nice sunroom off the kitchen overlooking the yard. The large fenced-in backyard provides plenty of privacy and space for outdoor activities, making it feel much larger than .85 acres.

Despite its secluded feel, this home is just minutes away from all the shopping, dining, and entertainment that Joplin has to offer.

With a roof only 5 years old and new water heater, all that's left to do is make this one yours.

Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity - call or text us to schedule your exclusive walkthrough today!
